@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Chat with GenAI Concierge

' =========================================================
' TEXT DESCRIPTION (Steps map to actions)
' Step 1  Renter opens chat.
' Step 2  Renter asks question or shares preferences.
' Step 3  System (GenAI) asks follow-up questions if needed.
' Step 4  System generates recommendations or answers.
' Step 5  System updates search criteria (extends Search & Filter).
' Step 6  System shows recommended listings.
' Step 7  Renter selects a listing or ends chat.
' =========================================================

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam DefaultFontSize 16
skinparam ArrowFontSize 14
skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 30

|Renter|
start
:1. Open concierge chat;
:2. Ask question / give preferences;

|System|
:3. Ask follow-up (if needed);

if (Need more info?) then (Yes)
  |Renter|
  :3. Provide missing details;
  |System|
  :3. Confirm preferences;
else (No)
endif

:4. Generate answer/recommendations;
:5. Update criteria\n(extends Search);
:6. Show recommended listings;

|Renter|
:7. Select listing\nor end chat;
stop

@enduml